80 ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::ModelBasedPlanningContext(const std::string& name,
81  const ModelBasedPlanningContextSpecification& spec)
82  : planning_interface::PlanningContext(name, spec.state_space_->getJointModelGroup()->getName())
83  , spec_(spec)
84  , complete_initial_robot_state_(spec.state_space_->getRobotModel())
85  , ompl_simple_setup_(spec.ompl_simple_setup_)
86  , ompl_benchmark_(*ompl_simple_setup_)
87  , ompl_parallel_plan_(ompl_simple_setup_->getProblemDefinition())
88  , ptc_(nullptr)
89  , last_plan_time_(0.0)
90  , last_simplify_time_(0.0)
91  , max_goal_samples_(0)
92  , max_state_sampling_attempts_(0)
93  , max_goal_sampling_attempts_(0)
94  , max_planning_threads_(0)
95  , max_solution_segment_length_(0.0)
96  , minimum_waypoint_count_(0)
97  , multi_query_planning_enabled_(false) // maintain "old" behavior by default
98  , simplify_solutions_(true)
99  , interpolate_(true)
100  , hybridize_(true)
101 {
102  complete_initial_robot_state_.update();
103 
104  constraints_library_ = std::make_shared<ConstraintsLibrary>(this);
105 }

107 void ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::configure(const ros::NodeHandle& nh, bool use_constraints_approximations)
108 {
109  loadConstraintApproximations(nh);
110  if (!use_constraints_approximations)
111  {
112  setConstraintsApproximations(ConstraintsLibraryPtr());
113  }
114  complete_initial_robot_state_.update();
115  ompl_simple_setup_->getStateSpace()->computeSignature(space_signature_);
116  ompl_simple_setup_->getStateSpace()->setStateSamplerAllocator(
117  std::bind(&ModelBasedPlanningContext::allocPathConstrainedSampler, this, std::placeholders::_1));
118 
119  // convert the input state to the corresponding OMPL state
120  ompl::base::ScopedState<> ompl_start_state(spec_.state_space_);
121  spec_.state_space_->copyToOMPLState(ompl_start_state.get(), getCompleteInitialRobotState());
122  ompl_simple_setup_->setStartState(ompl_start_state);
123  ompl_simple_setup_->setStateValidityChecker(ob::StateValidityCheckerPtr(new StateValidityChecker(this)));
124 
125  if (path_constraints_ && constraints_library_)
126  {
127  const ConstraintApproximationPtr& constraint_approx =
128  constraints_library_->getConstraintApproximation(path_constraints_msg_);
129  if (constraint_approx)
130  {
131  getOMPLStateSpace()->setInterpolationFunction(constraint_approx->getInterpolationFunction());
132  ROS_INFO_NAMED(LOGNAME, "Using precomputed interpolation states");
133  }
134  }
135 
136  useConfig();
137  if (ompl_simple_setup_->getGoal())
138  ompl_simple_setup_->setup();
139 }

141 void ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::setProjectionEvaluator(const std::string& peval)
142 {
143  if (!spec_.state_space_)
144  {
145  ROS_ERROR_NAMED(LOGNAME, "No state space is configured yet");
146  return;
147  }
148  ob::ProjectionEvaluatorPtr projection_eval = getProjectionEvaluator(peval);
149  if (projection_eval)
150  spec_.state_space_->registerDefaultProjection(projection_eval);
151 }

153 ompl::base::ProjectionEvaluatorPtr
154 ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::getProjectionEvaluator(const std::string& peval) const
155 {
156  if (peval.find_first_of("link(") == 0 && peval[peval.length() - 1] == ')')
157  {
158  std::string link_name = peval.substr(5, peval.length() - 6);
159  if (getRobotModel()->hasLinkModel(link_name))
160  return ob::ProjectionEvaluatorPtr(new ProjectionEvaluatorLinkPose(this, link_name));
161  else
162  ROS_ERROR_NAMED(LOGNAME,
163  "Attempted to set projection evaluator with respect to position of link '%s', "
164  "but that link is not known to the kinematic model.",
165  link_name.c_str());
166  }
167  else if (peval.find_first_of("joints(") == 0 && peval[peval.length() - 1] == ')')
168  {
169  std::string joints = peval.substr(7, peval.length() - 8);
170  boost::replace_all(joints, ",", " ");
171  std::vector<unsigned int> j;
172  std::stringstream ss(joints);
173  while (ss.good() && !ss.eof())
174  {
175  std::string joint;
176  ss >> joint >> std::ws;
177  if (getJointModelGroup()->hasJointModel(joint))
178  {
179  unsigned int variable_count = getJointModelGroup()->getJointModel(joint)->getVariableCount();
180  if (variable_count > 0)
181  {
182  int idx = getJointModelGroup()->getVariableGroupIndex(joint);
183  for (unsigned int q = 0; q < variable_count; ++q)
184  j.push_back(idx + q);
185  }
186  else
187  ROS_WARN_NAMED(LOGNAME, "%s: Ignoring joint '%s' in projection since it has 0 DOF", name_.c_str(),
188  joint.c_str());
189  }
190  else
191  ROS_ERROR_NAMED(LOGNAME,
192  "%s: Attempted to set projection evaluator with respect to value of joint "
193  "'%s', but that joint is not known to the group '%s'.",
194  name_.c_str(), joint.c_str(), getGroupName().c_str());
195  }
196  if (j.empty())
197  ROS_ERROR_NAMED(LOGNAME, "%s: No valid joints specified for joint projection", name_.c_str());
198  else
199  return ob::ProjectionEvaluatorPtr(new ProjectionEvaluatorJointValue(this, j));
200  }
201  else
202  ROS_ERROR_NAMED(LOGNAME, "Unable to allocate projection evaluator based on description: '%s'", peval.c_str());
203  return ob::ProjectionEvaluatorPtr();
204 }

206 ompl::base::StateSamplerPtr
207 ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::allocPathConstrainedSampler(const ompl::base::StateSpace* state_space) const
208 {
209  if (spec_.state_space_.get() != state_space)
210  {
211  ROS_ERROR_NAMED(LOGNAME, "%s: Attempted to allocate a state sampler for an unknown state space", name_.c_str());
212  return ompl::base::StateSamplerPtr();
213  }
214 
215  ROS_DEBUG_NAMED(LOGNAME, "%s: Allocating a new state sampler (attempts to use path constraints)", name_.c_str());
216 
217  if (path_constraints_)
218  {
219  if (constraints_library_)
220  {
221  const ConstraintApproximationPtr& constraint_approx =
222  constraints_library_->getConstraintApproximation(path_constraints_msg_);
223  if (constraint_approx)
224  {
225  ompl::base::StateSamplerAllocator state_sampler_allocator =
226  constraint_approx->getStateSamplerAllocator(path_constraints_msg_);
227  if (state_sampler_allocator)
228  {
229  ompl::base::StateSamplerPtr state_sampler = state_sampler_allocator(state_space);
230  if (state_sampler)
231  {
232  ROS_INFO_NAMED(LOGNAME,
233  "%s: Using precomputed state sampler (approximated constraint space) for constraint '%s'",
234  name_.c_str(), path_constraints_msg_.name.c_str());
235  return state_sampler;
236  }
237  }
238  }
239  }
240 
241  constraint_samplers::ConstraintSamplerPtr constraint_sampler;
242  if (spec_.constraint_sampler_manager_)
243  constraint_sampler = spec_.constraint_sampler_manager_->selectSampler(getPlanningScene(), getGroupName(),
244  path_constraints_->getAllConstraints());
245 
246  if (constraint_sampler)
247  {
248  ROS_INFO_NAMED(LOGNAME, "%s: Allocating specialized state sampler for state space", name_.c_str());
249  return ob::StateSamplerPtr(new ConstrainedSampler(this, constraint_sampler));
250  }
251  }
252  ROS_DEBUG_NAMED(LOGNAME, "%s: Allocating default state sampler for state space", name_.c_str());
253  return state_space->allocDefaultStateSampler();
254 }

256 void ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::useConfig()
257 {
258  const std::map<std::string, std::string>& config = spec_.config_;
259  if (config.empty())
260  return;
261  std::map<std::string, std::string> cfg = config;
262 
263  // set the distance between waypoints when interpolating and collision checking.
264  auto it = cfg.find("longest_valid_segment_fraction");
265  // If one of the two variables is set.
266  if (it != cfg.end() || max_solution_segment_length_ != 0.0)
267  {
268  // clang-format off
269  double longest_valid_segment_fraction_config = (it != cfg.end())
270  ? moveit::core::toDouble(it->second) // value from config file if there
271  : 0.01; // default value in OMPL.
272  double longest_valid_segment_fraction_final = longest_valid_segment_fraction_config;
273  if (max_solution_segment_length_ > 0.0)
274  {
275  // If this parameter is specified too, take the most conservative of the two variables,
276  // i.e. the one that uses the shorter segment length.
277  longest_valid_segment_fraction_final = std::min(
278  longest_valid_segment_fraction_config,
279  max_solution_segment_length_ / spec_.state_space_->getMaximumExtent()
280  );
281  }
282  // clang-format on
283 
284  // convert to string using no locale
285  cfg["longest_valid_segment_fraction"] = moveit::core::toString(longest_valid_segment_fraction_final);
286  }
287 
288  // set the projection evaluator
289  it = cfg.find("projection_evaluator");
290  if (it != cfg.end())
291  {
292  setProjectionEvaluator(boost::trim_copy(it->second));
293  cfg.erase(it);
294  }
295 
296  if (cfg.empty())
297  return;
298 
299  std::string optimizer;
300  ompl::base::OptimizationObjectivePtr objective;
301  it = cfg.find("optimization_objective");
302  if (it != cfg.end())
303  {
304  optimizer = it->second;
305  cfg.erase(it);
306 
307  if (optimizer == "PathLengthOptimizationObjective")
308  {
309  objective =
310  std::make_shared<ompl::base::PathLengthOptimizationObjective>(ompl_simple_setup_->getSpaceInformation());
311  }
312  else if (optimizer == "MinimaxObjective")
313  {
314  objective = std::make_shared<ompl::base::MinimaxObjective>(ompl_simple_setup_->getSpaceInformation());
315  }
316  else if (optimizer == "StateCostIntegralObjective")
317  {
318  objective = std::make_shared<ompl::base::StateCostIntegralObjective>(ompl_simple_setup_->getSpaceInformation());
319  }
320  else if (optimizer == "MechanicalWorkOptimizationObjective")
321  {
322  objective =
323  std::make_shared<ompl::base::MechanicalWorkOptimizationObjective>(ompl_simple_setup_->getSpaceInformation());
324  }
325  else if (optimizer == "MaximizeMinClearanceObjective")
326  {
327  objective =
328  std::make_shared<ompl::base::MaximizeMinClearanceObjective>(ompl_simple_setup_->getSpaceInformation());
329  }
330  else
331  {
332  objective =
333  std::make_shared<ompl::base::PathLengthOptimizationObjective>(ompl_simple_setup_->getSpaceInformation());
334  }
335 
336  ompl_simple_setup_->setOptimizationObjective(objective);
337  }
338 
339  // Don't clear planner data if multi-query planning is enabled
340  it = cfg.find("multi_query_planning_enabled");
341  if (it != cfg.end())
342  multi_query_planning_enabled_ = boost::lexical_cast<bool>(it->second);
343 
344  // check whether the path returned by the planner should be interpolated
345  it = cfg.find("interpolate");
346  if (it != cfg.end())
347  {
348  interpolate_ = boost::lexical_cast<bool>(it->second);
349  cfg.erase(it);
350  }
351 
352  // check whether solution paths from parallel planning should be hybridized
353  it = cfg.find("hybridize");
354  if (it != cfg.end())
355  {
356  hybridize_ = boost::lexical_cast<bool>(it->second);
357  cfg.erase(it);
358  }
359 
360  // remove the 'type' parameter; the rest are parameters for the planner itself
361  it = cfg.find("type");
362  if (it == cfg.end())
363  {
364  if (name_ != getGroupName())
365  ROS_WARN_NAMED(LOGNAME, "%s: Attribute 'type' not specified in planner configuration", name_.c_str());
366  }
367  else
368  {
369  std::string type = it->second;
370  cfg.erase(it);
371  const std::string planner_name = getGroupName() + "/" + name_;
372  ompl_simple_setup_->setPlannerAllocator(
373  std::bind(spec_.planner_selector_(type), std::placeholders::_1, planner_name, std::cref(spec_)));
374  ROS_INFO_NAMED(LOGNAME,
375  "Planner configuration '%s' will use planner '%s'. "
376  "Additional configuration parameters will be set when the planner is constructed.",
377  name_.c_str(), type.c_str());
378  }
379 
380  // call the setParams() after setup(), so we know what the params are
381  ompl_simple_setup_->getSpaceInformation()->setup();
382  ompl_simple_setup_->getSpaceInformation()->params().setParams(cfg, true);
383  // call setup() again for possibly new param values
384  ompl_simple_setup_->getSpaceInformation()->setup();
385 }

387 void ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::setPlanningVolume(const moveit_msgs::WorkspaceParameters& wparams)
388 {
389  if (wparams.min_corner.x == wparams.max_corner.x && wparams.min_corner.x == 0.0 &&
390  wparams.min_corner.y == wparams.max_corner.y && wparams.min_corner.y == 0.0 &&
391  wparams.min_corner.z == wparams.max_corner.z && wparams.min_corner.z == 0.0)
392  ROS_WARN_NAMED(LOGNAME, "It looks like the planning volume was not specified.");
393 
394  ROS_DEBUG_NAMED(LOGNAME,
395  "%s: Setting planning volume (affects SE2 & SE3 joints only) to x = [%f, %f], y = "
396  "[%f, %f], z = [%f, %f]",
397  name_.c_str(), wparams.min_corner.x, wparams.max_corner.x, wparams.min_corner.y, wparams.max_corner.y,
398  wparams.min_corner.z, wparams.max_corner.z);
399 
400  spec_.state_space_->setPlanningVolume(wparams.min_corner.x, wparams.max_corner.x, wparams.min_corner.y,
401  wparams.max_corner.y, wparams.min_corner.z, wparams.max_corner.z);
402 }

410 void ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::interpolateSolution()
411 {
412  if (ompl_simple_setup_->haveSolutionPath())
413  {
414  og::PathGeometric& pg = ompl_simple_setup_->getSolutionPath();
415 
416  // Find the number of states that will be in the interpolated solution.
417  // This is what interpolate() does internally.
418  unsigned int eventual_states = 1;
419  std::vector<ompl::base::State*> states = pg.getStates();
420  for (size_t i = 0; i < states.size() - 1; i++)
421  {
422  eventual_states += ompl_simple_setup_->getStateSpace()->validSegmentCount(states[i], states[i + 1]);
423  }
424 
425  if (eventual_states < minimum_waypoint_count_)
426  {
427  // If that's not enough states, use the minimum amount instead.
428  pg.interpolate(minimum_waypoint_count_);
429  }
430  else
431  {
432  // Interpolate the path to have as the exact states that are checked when validating motions.
433  pg.interpolate();
434  }
435  }
436 }

438 void ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::convertPath(const ompl::geometric::PathGeometric& pg,
439  robot_trajectory::RobotTrajectory& traj) const
440 {
441  moveit::core::RobotState ks = complete_initial_robot_state_;
442  for (std::size_t i = 0; i < pg.getStateCount(); ++i)
443  {
444  spec_.state_space_->copyToRobotState(ks, pg.getState(i));
445  traj.addSuffixWayPoint(ks, 0.0);
446  }
447 }

449 bool ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::getSolutionPath(robot_trajectory::RobotTrajectory& traj) const
450 {

454  return ompl_simple_setup_->haveSolutionPath();

463 ompl::base::GoalPtr ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::constructGoal()
464 {
465  // ******************* set up the goal representation, based on goal constraints
466 
467  std::vector<ob::GoalPtr> goals;
468  for (kinematic_constraints::KinematicConstraintSetPtr& goal_constraint : goal_constraints_)
469  {
470  constraint_samplers::ConstraintSamplerPtr constraint_sampler;
471  if (spec_.constraint_sampler_manager_)
472  constraint_sampler = spec_.constraint_sampler_manager_->selectSampler(getPlanningScene(), getGroupName(),
473  goal_constraint->getAllConstraints());
474  if (constraint_sampler)
475  {
476  ob::GoalPtr goal = ob::GoalPtr(new ConstrainedGoalSampler(this, goal_constraint, constraint_sampler));
477  goals.push_back(goal);
478  }
479  }
480 
481  if (!goals.empty())
482  return goals.size() == 1 ? goals[0] : ompl::base::GoalPtr(new GoalSampleableRegionMux(goals));
483  else
484  ROS_ERROR_NAMED(LOGNAME, "Unable to construct goal representation");
485 
486  return ob::GoalPtr();
487 }

489 ompl::base::PlannerTerminationCondition
490 ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::constructPlannerTerminationCondition(double timeout,
491  const ompl::time::point& start)
492 {
493  auto it = spec_.config_.find("termination_condition");
494  if (it == spec_.config_.end())
495  return ob::timedPlannerTerminationCondition(timeout - ompl::time::seconds(ompl::time::now() - start));
496  std::string termination_string = it->second;
497  std::vector<std::string> termination_and_params;
498  boost::split(termination_and_params, termination_string, boost::is_any_of("[ ,]"));
499 
500  if (termination_and_params.empty())
501  ROS_ERROR_NAMED(LOGNAME, "Termination condition not specified");
502  // Terminate if a maximum number of iterations is exceeded or a timeout occurs.
503  // The semantics of "iterations" are planner-specific, but typically it corresponds to the number of times
504  // an attempt was made to grow a roadmap/tree.
505  else if (termination_and_params[0] == "Iteration")
506  {
507  if (termination_and_params.size() > 1)
508  return ob::plannerOrTerminationCondition(
509  ob::timedPlannerTerminationCondition(timeout - ompl::time::seconds(ompl::time::now() - start)),
510  ob::IterationTerminationCondition(std::stoul(termination_and_params[1])));
511  else
512  ROS_ERROR_NAMED(LOGNAME, "Missing argument to Iteration termination condition");
513  }
514 // TODO: remove when ROS Melodic and older are no longer supported
515 #if OMPL_VERSION_VALUE >= 1005000
516  // Terminate if the cost has converged or a timeout occurs.
517  // Only useful for anytime/optimizing planners.
518  else if (termination_and_params[0] == "CostConvergence")
519  {
520  std::size_t solutions_window = 10u;
521  double epsilon = 0.1;
522  if (termination_and_params.size() > 1)
523  {
524  solutions_window = std::stoul(termination_and_params[1]);
525  if (termination_and_params.size() > 2)
526  epsilon = moveit::core::toDouble(termination_and_params[2]);
527  }
528  return ob::plannerOrTerminationCondition(
529  ob::timedPlannerTerminationCondition(timeout - ompl::time::seconds(ompl::time::now() - start)),
530  ob::CostConvergenceTerminationCondition(ompl_simple_setup_->getProblemDefinition(), solutions_window, epsilon));
531  }
532 #endif
533  // Terminate as soon as an exact solution is found or a timeout occurs.
534  // This modifies the behavior of anytime/optimizing planners to terminate upon discovering
535  // the first feasible solution.
536  else if (termination_and_params[0] == "ExactSolution")
537  {
538  return ob::plannerOrTerminationCondition(
539  ob::timedPlannerTerminationCondition(timeout - ompl::time::seconds(ompl::time::now() - start)),
540  ob::exactSolnPlannerTerminationCondition(ompl_simple_setup_->getProblemDefinition()));
541  }
542  else
543  ROS_ERROR_NAMED(LOGNAME, "Unknown planner termination condition");
544 
545  // return a planner termination condition to suppress compiler warning
546  return ob::plannerAlwaysTerminatingCondition();
547 }

556 void ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::clear()
557 {
558  if (!multi_query_planning_enabled_)
559  ompl_simple_setup_->clear();
560 // TODO: remove when ROS Melodic and older are no longer supported
561 #if OMPL_VERSION_VALUE >= 1005000
562  else
563  {
564  // For LazyPRM and LazyPRMstar we assume that the environment *could* have changed
565  // This means that we need to reset the validity flags for every node and edge in
566  // the roadmap. For PRM and PRMstar we assume that the environment is static. If
567  // this is not the case, then multi-query planning should not be enabled.
568  auto planner = dynamic_cast<ompl::geometric::LazyPRM*>(ompl_simple_setup_->getPlanner().get());
569  if (planner != nullptr)
570  planner->clearValidity();
571  }
572 #endif
573  ompl_simple_setup_->clearStartStates();
574  ompl_simple_setup_->setGoal(ob::GoalPtr());
575  ompl_simple_setup_->setStateValidityChecker(ob::StateValidityCheckerPtr());
576  path_constraints_.reset();
577  goal_constraints_.clear();
578  getOMPLStateSpace()->setInterpolationFunction(InterpolationFunction());
579 }

581 bool ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::setPathConstraints(const moveit_msgs::Constraints& path_constraints,
582  moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes* /*error*/)

584  // ******************* set the path constraints to use
585  path_constraints_ = std::make_shared<kinematic_constraints::KinematicConstraintSet>(getRobotModel());
586  path_constraints_->add(path_constraints, getPlanningScene()->getTransforms());
587  path_constraints_msg_ = path_constraints;
588

592 bool ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::setGoalConstraints(
593  const std::vector<moveit_msgs::Constraints>& goal_constraints, const moveit_msgs::Constraints& path_constraints,
594  moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes* error)
595 {
596  // ******************* check if the input is correct
597  goal_constraints_.clear();
598  for (const moveit_msgs::Constraints& goal_constraint : goal_constraints)
599  {
600  moveit_msgs::Constraints constr = kinematic_constraints::mergeConstraints(goal_constraint, path_constraints);
601  kinematic_constraints::KinematicConstraintSetPtr kset(
602  new kinematic_constraints::KinematicConstraintSet(getRobotModel()));
603  kset->add(constr, getPlanningScene()->getTransforms());
604  if (!kset->empty())
605  goal_constraints_.push_back(kset);
606  }
607 
608  if (goal_constraints_.empty())
609  {
610  ROS_WARN_NAMED(LOGNAME, "%s: No goal constraints specified. There is no problem to solve.", name_.c_str());
611  if (error)
612  error->val = moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::INVALID_GOAL_CONSTRAINTS;
613  return false;
614  }
615 
616  ob::GoalPtr goal = constructGoal();
617  ompl_simple_setup_->setGoal(goal);
618  return static_cast<bool>(goal);
619 }

659 void ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::preSolve()
660 {
661  // clear previously computed solutions
662  ompl_simple_setup_->getProblemDefinition()->clearSolutionPaths();
663  const ob::PlannerPtr planner = ompl_simple_setup_->getPlanner();
664  if (planner && !multi_query_planning_enabled_)
665  planner->clear();
666  startSampling();
667  ompl_simple_setup_->getSpaceInformation()->getMotionValidator()->resetMotionCounter();
668 }

670 void ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::postSolve()
671 {
672  stopSampling();
673  int v = ompl_simple_setup_->getSpaceInformation()->getMotionValidator()->getValidMotionCount();
674  int iv = ompl_simple_setup_->getSpaceInformation()->getMotionValidator()->getInvalidMotionCount();
675  ROS_DEBUG_NAMED(LOGNAME, "There were %d valid motions and %d invalid motions.", v, iv);
676 
677  if (ompl_simple_setup_->getProblemDefinition()->hasApproximateSolution())
678  ROS_WARN_NAMED(LOGNAME, "Computed solution is approximate");
679 }

681 bool ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::solve(planning_interface::MotionPlanResponse& res)
682 {
683  if (solve(request_.allowed_planning_time, request_.num_planning_attempts))
684  {
685  double ptime = getLastPlanTime();
686  if (simplify_solutions_)
687  {
688  simplifySolution(request_.allowed_planning_time - ptime);
689  ptime += getLastSimplifyTime();
690  }
691 
692  if (interpolate_)
693  interpolateSolution();
694 
695  // fill the response
696  ROS_DEBUG_NAMED(LOGNAME, "%s: Returning successful solution with %lu states", getName().c_str(),
697  getOMPLSimpleSetup()->getSolutionPath().getStateCount());
698 
699  res.trajectory_ = std::make_shared<robot_trajectory::RobotTrajectory>(getRobotModel(), getGroupName());
700  getSolutionPath(*res.trajectory_);
701  res.planning_time_ = ptime;
702  return true;
703  }
704  else
705  {
706  ROS_INFO_NAMED(LOGNAME, "Unable to solve the planning problem");
707  res.error_code_.val = moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::PLANNING_FAILED;
708  return false;
709  }
710 }
711 
712 bool ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::solve(planning_interface::MotionPlanDetailedResponse& res)
713 {
714  if (solve(request_.allowed_planning_time, request_.num_planning_attempts))
715  {
716  res.trajectory_.reserve(3);
717 
718  // add info about planned solution
719  double ptime = getLastPlanTime();
720  res.processing_time_.push_back(ptime);
721  res.description_.emplace_back("plan");
722  res.trajectory_.resize(res.trajectory_.size() + 1);
723  res.trajectory_.back() = std::make_shared<robot_trajectory::RobotTrajectory>(getRobotModel(), getGroupName());
724  getSolutionPath(*res.trajectory_.back());
725 
726  // simplify solution if time remains
727  if (simplify_solutions_)
728  {
729  simplifySolution(request_.allowed_planning_time - ptime);
730  res.processing_time_.push_back(getLastSimplifyTime());
731  res.description_.emplace_back("simplify");
732  res.trajectory_.resize(res.trajectory_.size() + 1);
733  res.trajectory_.back() = std::make_shared<robot_trajectory::RobotTrajectory>(getRobotModel(), getGroupName());
734  getSolutionPath(*res.trajectory_.back());
735  }
736 
737  if (interpolate_)
738  {
739  ompl::time::point start_interpolate = ompl::time::now();
740  interpolateSolution();
741  res.processing_time_.push_back(ompl::time::seconds(ompl::time::now() - start_interpolate));
742  res.description_.emplace_back("interpolate");
743  res.trajectory_.resize(res.trajectory_.size() + 1);
744  res.trajectory_.back() = std::make_shared<robot_trajectory::RobotTrajectory>(getRobotModel(), getGroupName());
745  getSolutionPath(*res.trajectory_.back());
746  }
747 
748  // fill the response
749  ROS_DEBUG_NAMED(LOGNAME, "%s: Returning successful solution with %lu states", getName().c_str(),
750  getOMPLSimpleSetup()->getSolutionPath().getStateCount());
751  return true;
752  }
753  else
754  {
755  ROS_INFO_NAMED(LOGNAME, "Unable to solve the planning problem");
756  res.error_code_.val = moveit_msgs::MoveItErrorCodes::PLANNING_FAILED;
757  return false;
758  }
759 }

761 bool ompl_interface::ModelBasedPlanningContext::solve(double timeout, unsigned int count)
762 {
763  moveit::tools::Profiler::ScopedBlock sblock("PlanningContext:Solve");
764  ompl::time::point start = ompl::time::now();
765  preSolve();
766 
767  bool result = false;
768  if (count <= 1 || multi_query_planning_enabled_) // multi-query planners should always run in single instances
769  {
770  ROS_DEBUG_NAMED(LOGNAME, "%s: Solving the planning problem once...", name_.c_str());
771  ob::PlannerTerminationCondition ptc = constructPlannerTerminationCondition(timeout, start);
772  registerTerminationCondition(ptc);
773  result = ompl_simple_setup_->solve(ptc) == ompl::base::PlannerStatus::EXACT_SOLUTION;
774  last_plan_time_ = ompl_simple_setup_->getLastPlanComputationTime();
775  unregisterTerminationCondition();
776  }
777  else
778  {
779  ROS_DEBUG_NAMED(LOGNAME, "%s: Solving the planning problem %u times...", name_.c_str(), count);
780  ompl_parallel_plan_.clearHybridizationPaths();
781  if (count <= max_planning_threads_)
782  {
783  ompl_parallel_plan_.clearPlanners();
784  if (ompl_simple_setup_->getPlannerAllocator())
785  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < count; ++i)
786  ompl_parallel_plan_.addPlannerAllocator(ompl_simple_setup_->getPlannerAllocator());
787  else
788  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < count; ++i)
789  ompl_parallel_plan_.addPlanner(ompl::tools::SelfConfig::getDefaultPlanner(ompl_simple_setup_->getGoal()));
790 
791  ob::PlannerTerminationCondition ptc = constructPlannerTerminationCondition(timeout, start);
792  registerTerminationCondition(ptc);
793  result = ompl_parallel_plan_.solve(ptc, 1, count, hybridize_) == ompl::base::PlannerStatus::EXACT_SOLUTION;
794  last_plan_time_ = ompl::time::seconds(ompl::time::now() - start);
795  unregisterTerminationCondition();
796  }
797  else
798  {
799  ob::PlannerTerminationCondition ptc = constructPlannerTerminationCondition(timeout, start);
800  registerTerminationCondition(ptc);
801  int n = count / max_planning_threads_;
802  result = true;
803  for (int i = 0; i < n && !ptc(); ++i)
804  {
805  ompl_parallel_plan_.clearPlanners();
806  if (ompl_simple_setup_->getPlannerAllocator())
807  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < max_planning_threads_; ++i)
808  ompl_parallel_plan_.addPlannerAllocator(ompl_simple_setup_->getPlannerAllocator());
809  else
810  for (unsigned int i = 0; i < max_planning_threads_; ++i)
811  ompl_parallel_plan_.addPlanner(ompl::tools::SelfConfig::getDefaultPlanner(ompl_simple_setup_->getGoal()));
812  bool r = ompl_parallel_plan_.solve(ptc, 1, count, hybridize_) == ompl::base::PlannerStatus::EXACT_SOLUTION;
813  result = result && r;
814  }
815  n = count % max_planning_threads_;
816  if (n && !ptc())
817  {
818  ompl_parallel_plan_.clearPlanners();
819  if (ompl_simple_setup_->getPlannerAllocator())
820  for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
821  ompl_parallel_plan_.addPlannerAllocator(ompl_simple_setup_->getPlannerAllocator());
822  else
823  for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
824  ompl_parallel_plan_.addPlanner(ompl::tools::SelfConfig::getDefaultPlanner(ompl_simple_setup_->getGoal()));
825  bool r = ompl_parallel_plan_.solve(ptc, 1, count, hybridize_) == ompl::base::PlannerStatus::EXACT_SOLUTION;
826  result = result && r;
827  }
828  last_plan_time_ = ompl::time::seconds(ompl::time::now() - start);
829  unregisterTerminationCondition();
830  }
831  }
832 
833  postSolve();
834 
835  return result;
836 }
